The interior ministry has announced the massive transfer of county commissioners as well as deputy county commissioners across the country.
A list released by the ministry showed that a whopping 34 deputy commissioners had been moved from their workstations and posted to other areas.
It was a total overhaul in Wajir County where the deputy commissioners of Wajir South, North and West were all transferred to Suba, Imenti South and Nyando respectively.



